                {
                    "name": "Slime",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "<b>Saving Throw</b> Fortitude DC 25; <b>Stage 1</b> no ill effect (1 round); <b>Stage 2</b> the victim\u2019s skin softens, inflicting drained 1 (1 round); <b>Stage 3</b> the victim\u2019s skin transforms into a clear, slimy membrane, inflicting drained 2 until the curse ends; every hour this membrane remains dry, the creature\u2019s drained condition increases by 1 (permanent). A <a aonid=\"251\" game-obj=\"Spells\">remove disease</a> spell can counteract this curse, but immunity to disease offers no protection against it.",
                    "subtype": "offensive_action",
                    "traits": [
                        {
                            "type": "stat_block_section",
                            "subtype": "trait",
